유저 토큰

앨범 관련

앨범 호출

HTTP request

GET /api/v1/album/1 HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json
Host: http://ec2-3-37-6-83.ap-northeast-2.compute.amazonaws.com
Table 1. /api/v1/album/{id}
Parameter Description

id

앨범 IDX

HTTP response

HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json
Content-Length: 1084

size

page
